==Japanese==
(まこと)

May be roughly translated as "sincerity".

=== Further Reading ===

* [http://www.ajjf.org/article04.html Makoto - Sincerity]

Makoto, normally a Japanese name for males, is sometimes used as a first name for females.  In the Japanese language, similar sounds can be represented by very different Kanji.  Whem Makoto is used for a female name it is broken into Ma = honest, sincere and Koto = the japanese 3 stringed tradional harp/guitar.